          "settings": {
            "heading": "Sizing Instructions:",
            "icon": "ruler",
            "content": "<h5>Measure 1/8th Inch Above The Ear.  Right where the hat band would normally sit.</h5><h5>Tape should be firm but not tight.  The tape should wrap straight across your mid-forehead.  Roughly one inch above your eyebrows.</h5><h5>Make sure it stays level all the way around your head (not dipping down behind your ears).</h5><h5>Check the sizing chart below.</h5><h5>If you are in between sizes, go with the bigger size.  </h5><h5>We will include sizers with each purchase, this can used to add up to tighten the hat for  SMALL adjustments if it is slightly too big.</h5><h5><strong>Any questions, Book a Free virtual consultation with the Book Now button and we will be happy to help you!</strong></h5>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
